Que: What is the DriverManager ? What are the basic work and methods of Driver Manager?
Sol: DriverManager is a class of that is the Key Component of the JDBC Architecture API. DriverManager class is present
     in the java.mysql package. DriverManager class is totally responsible to control the Diver Software and to
     established connectivity between the Java Application and the Data Bases.

  #DriverManagers Class basic methods:
  1. public static synchronized void registerDriver(Driver driver);   To register a driver
  2. public static synchronized void deregisterDriver(Driver driver); To deregistered a driver
  3. public static Connection getConnection(String url,String userName,String password) throws SQLException;
